title: DEXTER complete
description:
dexter morgan, everyones favourite serial killer, and star of teh greatest tv show known to man. here we have for your viewing pleasure both complete seasons of the hit showtime erm...show.

a small note...obviously you need xvid as you do with most downloaded moving pictures, your also gunna need ac3 and div3 codecs, theres a codec pack by some guy called nimo(or something) that contains these but it turned every video green and blippy....might just be the fact that my pc is a dell...or it might be a dodgey pack...either way your probably better off downloading them seperately. anyhoo enjoy the wonder that is dexter.
